<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
<h1>Welcome to Alpha Kappa Psi at Berkeley, <%= @rushee.name %></h1>
<p>
  You are now officially part of AKÎ¨ Alpha Beta Chapter's rush process.  <br/>
  Your username and password are as follows; <i>please place this information in a safe place as it will be required when you submit
  your rush application.</i> <br/>

  <br/>
  <b>Username:</b> <%= @rushee.email %>    <br/>
  <b>Password:</b> <%= @rushee.password %>      <br/>
  <br/>

  In addition, you'll receive updates and reminders about our rush events. Below is a quick breakdown of all planned events and their times:    <br/>

  <% for index in 0 ... @rush_events.size %>
    <br/>
      <b><%= @rush_events[index].event_name %></b> <br/>
      <i>Description: </i><%= @rush_events[index].event_description   %> <br/>
      <i>Time: </i><%= @rush_events[index].event_time.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %> <br/>
      <i>Location: </i><%= @rush_events[index].location  %> <br/>
  <% end %>

  <br/>
  To submit your rush application, go to <%= @url %>/rush and follow the instructions on the page.
  <br/>
  Thank you for your interest in Alpha Kappa Psi and the best of luck to you in the process.
  <br/>
</p>
<p>
  Feel free to check out our website here: <%= @url %>.
  If you would like to withdraw from the process, please click <%= link_to "here", @url %>.
</p>
</body>
</html>